e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"十八樓C座"},{"pid":"81375a61158199b9fb8eb0844c38bf649ac15033","tid":327201,"uid":11601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"日日都聽 俾frd話我成個阿叔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37757043662eebbdb7d4172e4973e2f3555d7822","tid":327201,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友話工作關係每日都要聽電台的時事節的，寫一份executive summary俾老闆參考「民情」。我心諗，仲有人聽電台架咩？慳返錢做網絡數據分析好過啦。</blockquote><br />\n睇民情要唔要聽埋本土台先？"},{"pid":"3d6bef3c06b846d7d3cd58396531ffd4af40e746","tid":327201,"uid":62309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朝朝搭車番工都會聽903點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有聽，朋友亦都係專做phone-in節目撮要。只是我覺得如果要準確掌握民情，電台唔夠網絡咁快、受眾亦無咁廣。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n網絡快既同時種類廣泛，但正正因為種類太多太廣，明明睇緊一單要聞，睇完之後好易越click 越遠。<br />\n<br />\n反而電台有主持圍繞幾個主題深入探討，好多時挑選出黎既題目同民生已經好有聯繫，好似903晴朗咁。"},{"pid":"bdaebc93b5845185562a5eea4fb11ad5748938bb","tid":327201,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>光明頂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4837b68f14378ba7a6d2a639eec2f20fd0376c","tid":327201,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"電台烽煙節目個輿論力量仲好強<br />\n但只限4張以上人士<br />\n後生嘅話上連登就知道哂"},{"pid":"31a280ba184049462f27aedf7908a4ac9176ca1a","tid":327201,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"光明頂！"},{"pid":"0fac3aad698c749a9f6f94ad7b1eba2820c1c05c","tid":327201,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"聽著光明頂答你"},{"pid":"1842f0386a2e21bc369da9414ccfff5b1dc0769e","tid":327201,"uid":26506,"